2004-09-16(plan)  Masahito Omote <omote@utyuuzin.net>
	* Release 0.13.
	* Porting to GTK+ 2.4. You have to install GTK+ >= 2.4.0 before
	  using sumika.
	* Change COPYRIGHT from GPL to BSD License see README for more
	  details.
	* gtk2/uimcontainer.c, common/uimconfig.c
	  - Drop hard coding into sumika and use uim custom API instead.
	  - Not work yet.
	
2004-05-11  Masahito Omote <omote@utyuuzin.net>
	* Release 0.12.
	* Use GtkSpinButton on frequecy field.
	* Use dynamic loding of libuim.so.0 and remove siod interface.
	  Thanks to YamaKen-san <yamaken@bp.iij4u.or.jp>.
	* Include config.h. By this change, most files are gettextized.
	* gtk2/charset.c: use g_utf8_validate before conversion.
	* include/cannadic.h: move #CN, #CNS, #JCN, #JNS, #JNM, #KK from
	  etc_code to substantive_code.

2004-04-10  Masahito Omote <omote@utyuuzin.net>
	* Release 0.11
	* Support NetBSD-current thanks to Yamashiro Jun.
	* Disable DISABLE_DEPRECATED compile flags, sumika does not port to
	  GTK+ 2.4 yet.
	* Show dialogs at the center.
	* gtk2/main.c
	  - Add #include <locale.h>.
	* gtk2/charset.c
	  - Return NULL when g_convert fails.
	* gtk2/topwin.c
	  - Fix hardcode version in about dialog.
	* gtk2/addwordpane.c
	  - Fix memory leak.
	  - Check NULL properly.
	* gtk2/anthyaddwordpane.c
	  - Fix conditional decision when registering word.
	  - Fix memory leak.
	  - Check NULL properly.
	* dixchange/dixchange.c
	  - Check NULL properly.
2004-02-13  Masahito Omote <omote@utyuuzin.net>
	* Release 0.10
	* Support uim configuration.
	  - Use siod for parsing ~/.uim. So this may makes sumika segv.
	  - Only supports static configuration.
	  - Dynamic configuraion is not implemented yet because uim does not
	    implement configuration via uim-helper-server now.
	* Change expression of verb example.
	* Fix miscellaneous bugs.
2004-01-02  Masahito Omote <omote@utyuuzin.net>
	* Release 0.07
	* Use Automake 1.7.
	* New feature
	  - Integrate mode(only adding words) support.
	  - Searching word support(Anthy Only).
	* Improve Option menu's handling.
	* Improve cannadic parser.
